\begin_layout Standard
定义要求极限值与 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta z\to0$
\end_inset

 的方向无关，特别是：沿实轴和虚轴所得的极限值应相等
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim\limits _{\Delta x\to0}\frac{u(x+\Delta x,y)+\mathrm{i}v(x+\Delta x,y)}{\Delta x}=\lim\limits _{\mathrm{i}\Delta y\to0}\frac{u(x,y+\Delta y)+\mathrm{i}v(x,y+\Delta y)}{\mathrm{i}\Delta y}
\]

\end_inset

比较实部和虚部，得到复变函数可导的必要条件：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[Cauchy--Riemann]
\end_layout

\end_inset

