\begin_inset Formula $w(z)$
\end_inset

 在点 
\begin_inset Formula $z\in D$
\end_inset

 处可导，则有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pdv{u}{x}=\pdv{v}{y}\qquad\pdv{u}{y}=-\pdv{v}{x}
\]

\end_inset

或等价的
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\pdv{w(z,z^{*})}{z^{*}}=0
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

